yeah sure , well you need to have a (wifi router) , and you need to portforwarded your router/wifi to port 43594 , and you can do this in your router/wifi settings, it will be named ( portforwarding or port range forwarding ) and put ur ip address in and the port 43594 , tcp and udp (both) and then click save , and re-run ur server and it should work
